description:
Anthony felt called to live a solitary life of prayer in the deserts of Egypt yet influenced an entire generation under persecution not to compromise the identity of Christ. 

Lost Legacy Reclaimed is a docudrama series about the early Christian Church in North Africa, its great leaders, teachers, and martyrs. Meet these faithful Christians from the first five centuries of church history who set a high standard for future generations by sacrificing for Jesus Christ during intense persecution from the Roman Empire and others.

Director: Denise Godwin
Starring Christopher Gornold-Smith, Angel L. Juste
